In the cos_samples directory:
- scripts to find a sample of Simba galaxies matching the COS-Halos and COS-Dwarfs criteria
- scripts to match galaxies selected in one wind box with galaxies in another wind box
- script to select the particles in our LOS and save these particle IDs to a new file
- script to save a new h5 dataset with only these particles
- scripts to call pygad and generate spectra of these LOS and save the output spectra

In the absorption_analysis directory:
- scripts to compute the equivalent width, covering fraction, path absorption, cosmic variance, etc.
- plotting scripts
